    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine, how could spirits and mythical creatures feel these days? What if they were closer, than it could seem? Perhaps, your classmate nearby or a guy selling you street food may appear as one of them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a story about Kot - a house spirit in the shape of a cat. It’s lost its owner and his powers leave him insensibly. It has to find a new owner to survive before they disappear. But what if he meets a lost kitten? Or a restless soul? Or a thirsting demon hunting the weakend hero’s energy remains?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here you can control the character’s fate and the events of the story. Make your choice, fights with demons, save kittens and punish villains  All in your paws.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250230/extras/f45a803bb45448ff638d71ac29626018.poster.avif?t=1769681130\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250230/extras/f45a803bb45448ff638d71ac29626018.webm?t=1769681130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings, non linear playthrough</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visual novel with interactive elements. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fairy tale characters in the modern world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as